headline: Morgan Stanley (MS): Fresh Analyst Upgrades Spark New Valuation Debate After Strong Wealth Management Growth
summary: Morgan Stanley (MS) just got a fresh boost after Wolfe Research upgraded the stock to "Outperform." This upgrade, along with renewed analyst optimism, spotlights the bank’s expanding market share and accelerating wealth management growth. See our latest analysis for Morgan Stanley. Morgan Stanley’s share price has been on a tear, climbing 34.6% year-to-date and posting a robust 31.6% total shareholder return over the past year.
